      isOpen ? 'bg-opacity-50 opacity-100' : 'bg-opacity-0 opacity-0 pointer-events-none'
    }`} onClick={onClose}>
      {/* Search overlay content */}
    </div>
  );
}

export default EnhancedMainNavigation;